[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0290","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0290.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0340","title":"SuSE Linux Gnomelib 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 6.3/6.4 的 Gnomelib 组件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序未对 DISPLAY 环境变量长度进行有效边界检查，本地攻击者可通过向该变量传递超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而以当前用户权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux 6.3 及 6.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0340"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.770","remediation":"升级 SuSE Linux 至 6.4 及以上版本，或安装 SuSE 官方提供的 Gnomelib 补丁包（可从 ftp.suse.com 获取）。临时缓解措施可限制本地用户设置 DISPLAY 环境变量的长度，或限制受影响系统的本地登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1155","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=00042902575201.09597%40wintermute-pub","http://www.suse.com/us/support/download/updates/axp_63.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19883","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0340.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0340","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0340.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0340.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7r2-2mff-xm27/GHSA-r7r2-2mff-xm27.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0340.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001326.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--97ad9843-21b0-4426-9018-a22266ea74ed.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0290.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0352","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0352.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0429","title":"McMurtrey Whitaker & Associates Cart32 后门密码远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cart32 是一款购物车管理软件，其 2.6 及 3.0 版本中存在硬编码后门密码漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该内置后门密码直接登录系统后台管理界面，进而执行任意系统命令，完全控制目标服务器。该漏洞利用复杂度低，攻击者只需通过网络访问即可触发，影响范围广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0429"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:42.837","remediation":"立即升级 Cart32 至 3.0a 及以上版本，该版本已移除默认后门管理员密码。若厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce），并在迁移前通过防火墙限制对 Cart32 管理端口的访问（默认端口 1001/tcp）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95686068203138&w=2","http://www.cart32.com/kbshow.asp?article=c048","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19881","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0429.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0429","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0429.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0429.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qr5c-3r3w-6h26/GHSA-qr5c-3r3w-6h26.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/c32.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0429.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0352.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0352.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0352.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0315","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0315.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0380","title":"Cisco IOS HTTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 11.1 至 12.1 版本的 HTTP 服务存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20）。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标路由器或交换机发送包含 `%%` 字符串的特制 URL 请求，即可触发该漏洞，导致设备 HTTP 服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响大量 Cisco 路由器和交换机设备，CVSS 评分 7.1，危害等级高。目前 Cisco 已发布安全公告，建议用户升级至不受影响的 IOS 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0380"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:35.753","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.1.5 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，可在全局配置模式下使用 `no ip http server` 命令禁用 HTTP 服务，或通过访问控制列表（ACL）限制仅允许可信管理 IP 访问 HTTP 服务（80/443 端口）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0261.html","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/707/ioshttpserver-pub.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/1302","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1154","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19882","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0380.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0380.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0380","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/ffab8835dab57629dd708bbd389c0fd0b4f23ace/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0380.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0380.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g22v-2gp9-xpmh/GHSA-g22v-2gp9-xpmh.json","https://github.com/Hepburnsunsir/poc-/blob/3303182f1e0caa3228cb2b3ce8cd9147b237c5b7/routersploit/routersploit/modules/exploits/routers/cisco/CVE-2000-0380-pl.py","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0315.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0315.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0315.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0225","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0225.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0249","title":"IBM AIX FRCA frcactrl 本地任意文件篡改漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统的快速响应缓存加速器（FRCA）中，frcactrl 程序在处理配置文件时存在不安全的文件操作缺陷。本地已登录的普通用户可利用该程序提供的配置功能，通过构造恶意参数对系统上任意文件进行篡改（如覆盖或写入关键系统文件）。该漏洞仅影响本地已获得系统访问权限的低权限用户，无法被远程直接利用，攻击条件是攻击者需先登录到目标 AIX 主机。成功利用后可导致系统文件完整性被破坏，进而可能引发权限提升或服务异常，危害本地系统安全。IBM 已通过相应的补丁程序修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0249"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-26","updated":"2000-04-26","remediation":"应用 IBM AIX 对应版本的安全补丁（APAR IY05850 等），升级至已修复的 AIX 4.3.3 维护级别或更高版本。临时缓解措施：使用 chmod 700 与 chown root:system 限制 frcactrl 程序权限，禁止普通用户执行；或通过 /etc/security/user 限制相关用户登录，关闭 FRCA 服务直至完成补丁升级。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1152","http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise47.php3","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0249.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0225.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0225.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0327","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0327.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0326","title":"Meeting Maker 密码弱加密漏洞","description":"Meeting Maker 使用多表代换密码对用户口令进行加密，该加密算法强度不足，存在弱加密漏洞。处于同一网段的远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探捕获加密后的口令数据包，并利用该弱加密算法的可预测性进行解密还原，从而获取明文口令，进而未授权访问 Meeting Maker 账户，危及系统数据安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0326"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:28.997","remediation":"Meeting Maker 已停止维护，无法通过官方补丁修复。建议立即迁移至支持强加密的现代日程管理软件（如 Microsoft Exchange/Outlook、Google Calendar）；作为临时缓解措施，所有客户端与服务器之间的连接应通过 VPN 或 SSH 隧道加密传输，避免密码在网络上以明文或弱加密形式暴露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.on.com/support/mmxp.nsf/31af51e08bcc93eb852565a90056138b/11af70407a16b165852568c50056a952?OpenDocument","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1151","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0326.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0326","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a632