\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16355,\"outputTokens\":42,\"totalTokens\":16397}}","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.2 的 Piranha 软件包中，Linux 虚拟服务器（LVS）的 Web 管理界面（GUI）存在一个硬编码的后门密码。该界面默认监听于特定端口并允许通过口令认证的远程用户执行系统命令。未经授权的远程攻击者在获知该后门密码后，可直接通过网络访问 Web GUI 并绕过正常身份验证，进而以服务运行权限在目标主机上执行任意命令，完全控制服务器。该漏洞影响安装了 Piranha 包且启用 LVS Web 管理功能的 Red Hat 6.2 系统，利用条件仅需网络可达目标端口并掌握后门口令，危害极大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0248"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:19.057","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Red Hat Linux 6.2 后续修复版本或应用官方安全补丁（RHSA-2000:047）。若无法立即升级，请修改 Piranha Web GUI 默认账户密码（用户名 piranha，默认密码 q），并在防火墙层面限制 3636 端口仅允许受信 IP 访问。建议停用不必要的 LVS Web 管理界面服务以彻底消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise46.php3","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19879","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9a9b6476a3f4a52ffa21ec6ed80d737eb0fc242b/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0248.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0248","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/ffab8835dab57629dd708bbd389c0fd0b4f23ace/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0248.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6f1dc1488b4a75cccf07339e6a0f0ab45fc38ad/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0248.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rr2-45q8-fjmg/GHSA-9rr2-45q8-fjmg.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/cve_2_MSF_exploit_Mapping/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/ad55126d2c24d81e3701e920d4bb2d7fd0fe1bd8/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/2d918d16364c8b9e6090c92b807ccd619223575d/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/piranha.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0709.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0709.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0709.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0336","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0336.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0334","title":"Allaire Spectra Container Editor 安全限制绕过漏洞","description":"Allaire Spectra 容器编辑器预览工具存在对象安全机制不严漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向容器对象中添加带有发布规则的对象方法来绕过权限限制，执行未授权的操作。该漏洞影响 Allaire Spectra 系列产品，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者利用此漏洞可进行非预期的内容操作，但攻击条件较为受限，需要目标系统启用容器编辑器预览功能。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0334"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.020","remediation":"建议升级至 Allaire Spectra 最新版本，并在容器编辑器中禁用预览工具（Preview Tool）的匿名访问权限，仅授予可信用户操作对象方法的权限。由于 Allaire 产品线已被 Adobe 收购并终止支持，建议迁移至 Adobe 或第三方受支持的替代内容管理系统，同时通过 Web 服务器访问控制列表限制对容器编辑器预览路径的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=15411&Method=Full","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1181","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0334.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0334","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0334.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0334.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2mm9-f8q6-86jx/GHSA-2mm9-f8q6-86jx.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0334.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001317.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0336.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0288","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0288.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0339","title":"Zone Labs ZoneAlarm 个人防火墙 UDP 端口 67 过滤绕过漏洞","description":"Zone Labs ZoneAlarm 2.1.10 及更早版本的个人防火墙存在安全策略绕过漏洞。该防火墙未正确过滤源端口为 67（DHCP 服务端口）的 UDP 数据包，远程攻击者可利用此缺陷，通过发送源端口为 67 的特制 UDP 报文绕过防火墙规则，直接与目标系统内部服务通信，从而实施进一步攻击。该漏洞影响 ZoneAlarm 2.1.10 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布更新版本修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0339"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.653","remediation":"升级 ZoneAlarm 至 2.1.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复 UDP 源端口 67 绕过防火墙的缺陷；如无法升级，在防火墙自定义规则中添加对 UDP 源端口 67 入站流量的过滤拦截，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1294","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1137","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=20000421044123.2353.qmail%40securityfocus.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19871","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0339.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0339","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-