chives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0188.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19876","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0337.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0337","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0337.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0337.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jmw3-v7qc-2gx9/GHSA-jmw3-v7qc-2gx9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0337.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--398c3ef0-479c-476b-b1d6-74c36998956f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0283.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0267","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0267.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0322","title":"Red Hat Piranha Virtual Server Package passwd.php3 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"Red Hat Piranha 虚拟服务器套件中的 passwd.php3 CGI 脚本存在命令注入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在输入参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）绕过输入过滤，以 Web 服务器进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Piranha Virtual Server Package 相关版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需拥有本地访问权限即可利用，Metasploit 框架已集成对应利用模块。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0322"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:28.470","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Piranha Virtual Server Package 至 0.4.13-1 及以上版本，该版本已对 passwd.php3 的输入参数进行转义处理，阻止 shell 元字符注入。如无法升级，建议移除或重命名 passwd.php3 脚本，或通过 Apache 配置 `<Files \"passwd.php3\"> Deny from all </Files>` 限制访问，并在 PHP 配置中启用 `safe_mode` 和禁用 `exec`/`system` 等危险函数。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至现代负载均衡方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2000-014.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1149","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Enip.BSO.23.0004241601140.28851-100000%40www.whitehats.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16858","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0322.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0322","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/ffab8835dab57629dd708bbd389c0fd0b4f23ace/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0322.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0322.json","https://github.com/gottburgm/Exploits/blob/fd340a05cbec416e89bfae898e27bf5fcb429101/MSFExploits/PIRANHA/MSF/PasswdExec_infos.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cxxx-c74v-hjm6/GHSA-cxxx-c74v-hjm6.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/2d918d16364c8b9e6090c92b807ccd619223575d/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0267.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0266","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0266.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0317","title":"Solaris lpset 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中 lpset 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 -r 选项传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，导致内存破坏，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 及 7.0 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账号才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0317"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:27.843","remediation":"升级至 Oracle Solaris 8 或更高版本，或应用相应补丁集补丁。如短期内无法升级，应通过文件权限管理移除 lpset 的 setuid 权限（chmod -s /usr/bin/lpset），或通过 RBAC（基于角色的访问控制）限制普通用户执行 lpset 命令的权限，仅允许授权管理员操作，防止本地提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0192.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0236.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95729763119559&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1138","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19874","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0317.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0317","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0317.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0317.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jhp4-7rfr-4p9v/GHSA-jhp4-7rfr-4p9v.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0317.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1138/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4f424782-69a1-4bf0-abf0-c864d936a21b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0266.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0265","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0265.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0316","title":"Sun Solaris lp -d 选项本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 及 7.0 系统中的 lp 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当使用超长参数传递给 -d 选项时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出。本地攻击者通过构造特制的 -d 参数执行 lp 命令，能够覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 与 7.0 版本，需要本地用户身份才能利用，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0316"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:27.727","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 106235-01（Solaris 7）或 106236-01（Solaris 2.6），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。如无法升级，可移除 lp 命令的 setuid 权限：chmod 755 /usr/bin/lp，但会导致普通用户无法使用打印功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0191.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1143","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19878","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0316.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0316","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0316.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0316.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-38cr-66jj-phh5/GHSA-38cr-66jj-phh5.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/solaris26_x86_106236.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0316.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/solaris7_x86_107116.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0265.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0322","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0322.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0321","title":"IC Radius 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IC Radius 软件包存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送包含超长用户名的认证请求触发该漏洞，导致服务崩溃和拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行受影响版本 IC Radius 软件的系统，攻击者仅需通过网络向 RADIUS 认证端口发送特制请求即可完成利用，造成服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0321"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-24","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"IC Radius 软件包已停止维护，无法通过官方升级修复该漏洞。建议在 RADIUS 服务前端部署入侵检测规则，对超过 64 字节的 User-Name 属性进行拦截丢弃；并将 RADIUS 服务绑定至内网接口，避免暴露在公网。如条件允许，应迁移至仍在维护的 RADIUS 实现（如 FreeRADIUS 或 GNU Radius）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0190.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1147","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0321"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0322.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0319","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0319.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0319","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail mail.local 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.10.x 版本中的 mail.local 组件未能正确识别标识邮件正文结束的 \".\\n\" 字符串，远程攻击者可通过发送一条长度为 2047 字符且以 \".\\n\" 结尾的特制邮件消息行，触发该解析缺陷，导致目标系统拒绝服务或邮箱数据损坏。该漏洞影响 Sendmail 8.9.3 及更早版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0319"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:28.097","remediation":"建议将 Sendmail 升级至 8.11.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 mail.local 中 fgets() 对超过 2047 字节消息行及结尾 .\\n 分隔符的识别缺陷。如无法立即升级，可应用 Sendmail 官方针对 mail.local 的 RELENG_8_10 分支补丁，或在邮件服务器前端对输入消息长度进行限制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1146","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=2694.000424%40SECURITY.NNOV.RU","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0319.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0319","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0319.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0319.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rc63-j49f-5vh2/GHSA-rc63-j49f-5vh2.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/sendmail_maillocal_dos.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/da